# Bike Service Slot Booking System

A responsive web application for booking bike service slots online.
Designed for service centers to manage customer appointments efficiently.

## Features
- Bike service slot booking form
- Date & time slot selection
- Mobile-friendly responsive UI
- Clean and simple UX
- Easy backend integration (PHP / Node.js / Firebase)

## Tech Stack
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## Use Cases
- Bike service centers
- Vehicle maintenance shops
- Appointment-based businesses

## Future Enhancements
- Admin dashboard
- Slot availability logic
- Payment integration
- Email & SMS notifications

